Extend Revenue Lifecycle Management With Custom Field Support
Customize Prices for Different Types of Transactions
Craft Professional Quote Documents with Document Builder
Get Better Cost Estimates by Including Tax Information on Orders
Easily Submit Orders for Fulfillment

Enhance the selling experience with Transaction Line Editor enhancements. Use custom fields to extend Revenue Lifecycle Management. Display unique prices depending on the type of transaction. Generate professional quote documents with Document Builder in Revenue Lifecycle Management. Estimate the tax on your orders. Submit orders to Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator for fulfillment or automatically submit eligible orders for fulfillment.

Transaction Line Editor
Customize the transaction experience for partner users. Manage transactions better with enhancements to the Transaction Line Editor. Know when prices in a transaction are inaccurate and easily refresh them.
Extend Revenue Lifecycle Management With Custom Field Support
Revenue Lifecycle Management now supports custom field mapping for operations such as quote creation, order creation, asset creation, asset update, and contract creation. Add custom fields to Revenue Lifecycle Management objects. Map the custom fields between objects in the transaction lifecycle for your sales reps.

Customize Prices for Different Types of Transactions
Trigger different pricing procedures based on the type of transaction by using the Sales Transaction Type object. For each type of transaction, create Sales Transaction Type records and assign pricing procedures to them.

Craft Professional Quote Documents with Document Builder
Give your quote documents an enhanced and professional look by using the capabilities of Document Builder. Use the branding of documents, embedded images, document preview, and the PDF generation features, to ensure that your documents reflect your business goals and meet your customer needs.

Get Better Cost Estimates by Including Tax Information on Orders
Sales reps, partners, and customers can now view estimated taxes on their orders. When an order is created from a quote, the tax information from the quote is automatically copied to the order.

Easily Submit Orders for Fulfillment
To submit orders to Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator for fulfillment, use the submitOrder invocable action from flows or Apex classes.

New and Changed Objects in Quote and Order Capture
Access more data through these new objects and fields.
New Invocable Action in Quote and Order Capture
Use the new invocable action in Quote and Order Capture.
New Metadata Type in Quote and Order Capture
Quote and Order Capture includes a new metadata type to create a contract from quote record.
